# Decisions log

> Append-only. PM and architect write entries here for every non-trivial decision.

Format:

```
## YYYY-MM-DD — <one-line decision>
- **By:** @<handle>
- **Context:** <one line — what triggered the decision>
- **Options considered:** <bullets>
- **Chosen:** <option>
- **Why:** <one to three sentences>
- **Reversible?** yes | no | yes-with-cost
- **Links:** <issue, PR, architecture doc>
```
